# 🚨 SOC250 - APT35 HyperScrape Data Exfiltration
**Severity:** High  
**Category:** Data Exfiltration  
**Threat Actor:** APT35 (Charming Kitten)  

## 📌 Summary
On December 27, 2023, a security alert (SOC250) was triggered indicating execution of a known APT35 (Charming Kitten) tool, Hyperscrape, on host Arthur (172.16.17[.]72).

Investigation revealed:
- Suspicious RDP login from external IP (173.209.51.54)
- Execution of malicious file: EmailDownloader.exe
- Email data extraction activity via OWA
- Outbound connection to malicious IP (136.243.108.14)

This activity is consistent with **email exfiltration using Hyperscrape**.

